                      <span class="ml-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">¿Necesita asistente para comunicarse?</span>
                    </label>

                    <label class="flex items-center p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50 cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-amber-300 transition-all">
